public class FosstrakInteropTestCase
extends org.dbunit.JdbcBasedDBTestCase

All test cases that require a clean state of the database should inherit from this class. Doing so ensures that before running each test case the database is reset with a predefined set of data. If you want to execute a database operation other that DatabaseOperation.CLEAN_INSERT then you should override getSetUpOperation().

Author:
Marco Steybe
